RECOGNIZE WEAPON QUALITY: Judging a weapon's craftsmanship

Category: Trade
Base skill: 25% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Examining a weapon and judging its true craftsmanship, condition, and
worth at a glance: whether it is a masterwork piece, a reliable
working weapon, or barely-functional junk dressed up to look better
than it is.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

